      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;lead !mb-9 text-xl&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Overview of &amp;ldquo;Gauntlet of Ageon&amp;rdquo;.&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Overview. &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#overview&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Gauntlet of Ageon &lt;em&gt;(a.k.a GoA)&lt;/em&gt; is a &lt;strong&gt;dungeon crawler, roguelike&lt;/strong&gt; game.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;It is being developed in the lua game framework &lt;a href=&#34;https://love2d.org&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Love2d&amp;rdquo;&lt;/a&gt;, with sprites made in &lt;a href=&#34;https://aseprite.io&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Aseprite&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;and music made in &lt;a href=&#34;https://yurisizov.itch.io/boscaceoil-blue&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Bosca Ceoil Blue&amp;rdquo;&lt;/a&gt;. The game is still in a very raw state &lt;em&gt;(02/12/2024 18:19:32)&lt;/em&gt; and is being developed only by me.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;The source code will be avaliable in github under the &lt;a href=&#34;https://opensource.org/license/mit&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;MIT License&lt;/a&gt; for anyone to use the code for learning, modding or inspiring purposes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
